         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1626, recto: (1) A reckoned tremis (2) has come to me (3) from you, Mena (son of) Peter, (4) as your share of xenion (5) and the other assessments (6) in the fifth year, (7) total one-third solidus.  Tybi 22, indiction 5.  (8) Pcher (son of) Athanasius (9) signs.  (10) Mena (son of) Paam (signs).</ab>
